      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections, while the interior is pristine with no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and all systems functioning exactly as designed. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality example that needs nothing but a new owner.",
