    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration experts! This car is ready for a second lease on life and represents an incredible project opportunity. While it is currently in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic repairs, it\u2019s a fantastic chance to build a vehicle exactly to your specifications. If you love getting your hands dirty and bringing a classic back to its former glory, this is the perfect canvas for you!",
